title: Placer County Deputies Locate Missing Snowboarder

organizations.name: tahoe nordic search and rescue team

text:
TAHOE CITY, CALIF, (CBS13) — Roughly an hour after reporting 32-year-old Ian Creelman missing at Alpine Meadows Ski Resort, Placer County Deputies located the man three miles south of Blackwood Canyon.
Tahoe Nordic Search and Rescue Team are currently hiking IanCreelman back out of the back country.
Deputies described his conditions and “cold and hungry,” but no serious injuries were reported.
